                       "message":  "ai-dispatch ISSUE-182: Add Codex stall watchdog to Invoke-WithTimeout\n\nUnattended dispatch run via Invoke-AiDispatchQueue.ps1.\nLoop exit code: 0. Control verdict: pass. Outcome: ok.\nSource: https://github.com/RustCADs/RGE/issues/182\nDetailed log: ai_dispatch_logs/log_2026-05-25_21-01-11+0300.md\n\nPublish policy: auto-push to origin/main only when loop exit code is 0 and\nCodex control verdict is pass. Failed or blocked work remains local.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
